ai.grakn.factory

Class OrientDBInternalFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.grakn.factory.OrientDBInternalFactory

  • public class OrientDBInternalFactory
extends Object

    A Grakn Graph on top of OrientGraph

    This produces an grakn graph on top of OrientGraph. The base construction process defined by AbstractInternalFactory ensures the graph factories are singletons.

    Author:
    fppt
